longBusinessSummary: Lithoquest Resources Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mining properties. It holds a 100% interest in the North Kimberley diamond project located in the King George River region of Western Australia. Lithoquest Resources Inc. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
